window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>#1 </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> bestselling author Dean Koontz’s brilliantly thrilling novel of suspense.</b></p> <p>In the midst of a raging blizzard, lightning struck on the night Laura Shane was born. And a mysterious blond-haired stranger showed up just in time to save her from dying.&nbsp;</p> <p>Years later, in the wake of another storm, Laura will be saved again. For someone is watching over her. Is he the guardian angel he seems? The devil in disguise? Or the master of a haunting destiny beyond all time and space?</p> <p><b>“A gripping novel...fast-paced and satisfying.” - </b><b><i>People</i></b></p>"; 
